113
00:07:45,636 --> 00:07:48,280
♪I'm the fog born in the forest♪

114
00:07:48,283 --> 00:07:50,807
♪You're the wind that rises at dusk♪

115
00:07:50,807 --> 00:07:55,890
♪If I become shattered anywhere you go,♪

116
00:07:55,970 --> 00:07:59,025
♪Disappearing into the forest with you♪

117
00:07:59,178 --> 00:08:04,610
